@page
@model Biobanks.Directory.Pages.Error

<head>
  <title>Error</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    
    <h2>
      We're sorry.<br/>
      <small>Something seems to have gone wrong.</small>
    </h2>
            
    <p>Your request caused an error.</p>
        
    <h3>How could this have happened?</h3>
    <p>Something technical went wrong.</p>
    <p>
      This may have been the result of one of the following:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>We might have moved the page you were trying to reach.</li>
      <li>You may have accidentally typed the wrong URL in the address bar.</li>
      <li>A previously undiscovered bug might have occurred when trying to process your request.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>What can I do now?</h3>
                    
    <ul>
      <li>You could verify the logged in user is you (at the top right of this page).</li>
      <li>You could try logging out and logging back in again</li>
      <li>You could use the navigation above to get back to where you were, and try again.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
